there are 2 sections of the project


1) Model creation and tuning part


2) Mapping the model binary object to REST API endpoint






USER:

check whether a loan application is to be accepted or rejected

1) Go to a website where our service is available (URL or IP address)
2) EITHER BY USING AN INTERFACE OR BY UPLOADING DATA, user will provide features 
of new customers (X_test)
3) submit the input
4) model will receive this input through an API end-point*
5) Model will make a prediction and generate an answer for each input
6) the answers will be converted into a JSON form and rendered on the UI using 
the user Interface!